Author: spacecatswillwin
Text: He’s a chef so he usually does the cooking anyways but he wants to do something special. Kinda think he’s going to propose tbh because we’ve already decided we are getting married next year and he has the ring so I’m trying to focus on that and not the food

Author: SweatshirtHoe
Text: You could bring up the possibility of cooking together so you might be able to have a little more control over everything
